---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import JsonLd from '~/components/JsonLd.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy — Tastatur und Maus e.V."
  description="Privacy policy for tastatur-und-maus.net. Statically hosted, no cookies, no tracking, no third-party CDN — contact submissions processed only to reply."
  locale="en"
>
  <JsonLd slot="head" locale="en" />
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p><strong>Controller.</strong> Tastatur und Maus e. V., Landstraße 35, 69502 Hemsbach, Germany. Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@tastatur-und-maus.net">privacy@tastatur-und-maus.net</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>What this site collects.</strong> This website is statically generated and self-hosted. It sets no cookies, runs no analytics, and makes no third-party network requests. Fonts, images, and all other assets are served from our own infrastructure.</p>
    <p>Your browser transmits technical request data (IP address, user agent, timestamp) to our web server in the normal course of any HTTP request. This data is kept briefly in server logs for operational and security purposes (legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR — legitimate interest in secure operation) and is not linked to any other dataset.</p>
    <p><strong>Email contact.</strong> If you write to any of the email addresses listed on this site, your message and contact details are processed only to answer you (Art. 6 (1) (b) GDPR).</p>
    <p><strong>Your rights.</strong> Under the GDPR you may request access, rectification, restriction, erasure, and data portability. You may object to processing and lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.</p>
    <p><strong>Supervisory authority.</strong> Der Landesbeauftragte für den Datenschutz und die Informationsfreiheit Baden-Württemberg, Lautenschlagerstraße 20, 70173 Stuttgart, <a href="https://www.baden-wuerttemberg.datenschutz.de">www.baden-wuerttemberg.datenschutz.de</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Revision event data.</strong> For data handled during Revision attendance (registration, photography, livestream, Partymeister), see the Revision privacy policy at <a href="https://revision-party.net/privacy/">revision-party.net/privacy/</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { max-width: 720px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 0 40px; }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px); margin-bottom: 32px; }
  p { margin: 14px 0; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-ink-2); }
</style>
